_sText:
NOTE: This map is still in beta.  I may make improvements to this version!  You can follow my WIP post to stay updated on the other game modes of this map I will be making(de, scouts, and zm).

**It is important that you set mat_colorcorrection to 1 in console for improved visuals**


The epic final stand on top of Mercy Hospital is now made for CSS!  I made everything from scratch (I did not port anything or copy and paste).  Feel free to leave constructive feedback!

2/8/2012:

The scout version is now complete, you can download it [here](http://www.gamebanana.com/css/maps/163528 "scout")

ZM and hopefully de on the way!
